  "content": "<p></p><h1 class=\"title\"><img src=\"http://www.aonprd.com/images/PathfinderSocietySymbol.gif\" style=\"margin:3px 3px 0px 3px\" title=\"PFS Legal\" /> Lorris</h1><h2><b>The Savior Hound</b></h2><b>Source</b> <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"http://paizo.com/products/btpy94wj?Pathfinder-Campaign-Setting-Inner-Sea-Gods-Hardcover\" target=\"_blank\"><i>Inner Sea Gods pg. 322</i></a><br /><b>Pathfinder Wiki</b> <a href=\"http://www.pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Lorris\">Lorris</a><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Details</h3><p><b>Alignment</b> NG<br /><b>Pantheon</b> Empyreal Lords<br /><b>Areas of Concern</b> Charity, the disadvantaged, volunteering<br /><b>Domains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Community\">Community</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Good\">Good</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Liberation\">Liberation</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Protection\">Protection</a><br /><b>Subdomains</b> <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Good\">Agathion</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Protection\">Defense</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Community\">Family</a>, <a href=\"DomainDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Liberation\">Freedom</a><br /><i>* Requires the <u><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Acolyte%20of%20Apocrypha\">Acolyte of Apocrypha</a></u> trait.</i><br /><b>Favored Weapon</b> Shortspear<br /><b>Symbol</b> Howling dog on coin<br /><b>Sacred Animal(s)</b> Hound<br /><b>Sacred Color(s)</b> Brown, gold<br /></p><h2 class=\"title\">For Followers of Lorris</h2><p></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Feats</h3><p><a href=\"FeatDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Heroic Interposition\">Heroic Interposition</a></p><h3 class=\"framing\">Traits</h3><p><a href=\"TraitDisplay.aspx?ItemName=Empyreal Focus\">Empyreal Focus</a><br /><br /></p><div style=\"position:relative;left:0%;border:2px ridge #434343;width:100%;height:100%\"><div class=\"wiki-content-full\"><iframe style=\"overflow-y:hidden;width:100%;height:450px\" src=\"https://pathfinderwiki.com/wiki/Lorris\"> </iframe></div>\n </div>",
